{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~pazzani/Slides/Hill/sld004.htm", "content": "\r\n<!--  Presentation generated by Internet Assistant for Microsoft PowerPoint 97 -->\r\n\r\n<HTML>\r\n<HEAD>\r\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Context-Type\" CONTEXT=\"text/html;charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Microsoft Internet Assistant for Microsoft PowerPoint 97\">\r\n <TITLE>Hill Climbing Search</TITLE> \r\n</HEAD>\r\n\r\n<BODY     >\r\n\r\n<CENTER>\r\n<TABLE WIDTH=100%> \r\n     <TR> <TD WIDTH=100% ALIGN=CENTER>\r\n         <IMG SRC=\"img004.GIF\" usemap=\"#Objmap\" WIDTH=640 HEIGHT=480 BORDER=0>\r\n     </TD> </TR>\r\n     <TR> <TD WIDTH=100% ALIGN=CENTER>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld001.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"first.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"First\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld003.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"prev.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Previous\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld005.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"next.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Next\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld039.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"last.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Last\"></A>\r\n         <IMG SRC=\"space.gif\" BORDER=0>\r\n         <A HREF=\"index.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"info.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Index\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~pazzani\"><IMG SRC=\"home.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Home\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"tsld004.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"text.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Text\"></A>\r\n     </TD> </TR>\r\n</TABLE>\r\n<P>Slide 4 of 39</P>\r\n</CENTER>\r\n<!-- <UL>\r\n<H2>Hill Climbing Search</H2>\r\n<BR></UL></P>\r\n<P><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Given\r\n</H2>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>I\tInitial state\r\n<LI>O\tOperators (Functions that map one state into another)\r\n<LI>E A state evaluation function\r\n</UL></UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Produce\r\n</H2>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>A new state, reached by some sequence of operator applications, that improves upon the current state</UL></UL></P>\r\n<P><UL>\r\n1. State = I\r\n<BR></UL><UL>\r\n2. Score = E(State)\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n3. BestState = False\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n4. Loop for Operator in O\r\n<UL>\r\na. Next = Operator(State)\r\n<BR><BR>b. NextScore = E(Next)\r\n<BR>c. When NextScore &#062 Score\r\n<UL>\r\nScore = NextScore\r\n<BR><BR>BestState = Next\r\n</UL></UL></UL><UL>\r\n5. If BestState = False\r\n<UL>\r\nThen Return(State)\r\n<BR><BR>Else GoTo 2</UL></UL></P>\r\n<P>  -->\r\n</Body>\r\n</HTML>\r\n", "encoding": "ascii"}